Class Component

java.lang.Object
eu.mihosoft.freerouting.board.Component
All Implemented Interfaces:
ObjectInfoPanel.Printable, UndoableObjects.Storable, Serializable, Comparable<Object>
public class Component extends Object implements UndoableObjects.Storable, ObjectInfoPanel.Printable, Serializable
Describes board components consisting of an array of pins und other stuff like component keepouts.
